'''熱狗麵包'''是加了[[熱狗|熱狗]]的[[麵包|麵包]]，麵包是特別為了夾熱狗設計的長式軟麵包。用麵包夾住熱狗，讓吃的人不會因熱狗太熱而燙到手<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A1021834] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20120720033216/http://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A1021834 |date=2012-07-20 }} "The Evolution of Hot Dogs", May 8, 2003 accessed January 29, 2011.</ref>。 

在美國，最常見的熱狗麵包是在麵包側邊開口，放入熱狗及調味料，但在長麵包一端開口，放入熱狗的{{le|新英格蘭式熱狗麵包|New England-style hot dog bun}}在新英格蘭地區也很流行<ref>[https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/food-dining/2013/07/02/top-loading-buns-typical-new-england-for-lobster-and-clams/QiEC0fUGxJl2MwNizjYxdL/story.html] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/food-dining/2013/07/02/top-loading-buns-typical-new-england-for-lobster-and-clams/QiEC0fUGxJl2MwNizjYxdL/story.html |date=20210309164309 }} "New England-style bun, from HoJo’s to homemade", July 2, 2013 accessed February 12, 2014.</ref>。其他地區也有一些變化，例如[[芝加哥式热狗|芝加哥式热狗]]會在麵包中加入[[罌粟籽|罌粟籽]]。

